<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Sangmuol A Liem Tau</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. I hinkhuou leh ninnuom puon bang chulsa,
 Pak bang tuoiin sangmuol a liem zo tai;
 Mu bang ngaiin nau bang kap mahleng le,
 Lenthang kumkhuo zatam in ei hal tai.

[V2]
 2. Muikhuo zina chung sawl tha vak nuoia,
 Theisen lawm guol nau bang kilawp lai kha;
 Zamuol liemin chung thangvan tuol nuom ah,
 Hai bang ei ngak, ngaih lenpul do mah leng.

[V3]
 3. Hun leh phat kum sang a hung beih tieng leh,
 Zuo min lun sietlei leh thangvan Siempa'n;
 Hinkhuo ninnuoma lenpul I do hih,
 Tuoi theilo in puon bang ei vuk ina.

[V4]
 4. Ka hun pakchau lenthang kumkhuo kihei,
 Khanno guol di'n vangphatna hung hi'n la;
 Zatam ma lo tui bangin hung nem hen,
 Kumsul veisa thavang ngailo dingin.</lyrics>
<author>Vankhama</author>
<hymn_number>271</hymn_number>
</song>